title: Spring into your Dream Home!
posting_body: Groveland Manor welcomes all newcomers and current residents with warmth and respect from our professionally managed and beautifully maintained community.
Our gorgeous country setting provides for a quiet and active lifestyle.
We offer a pool, basketball court, playground, dog walk area, boat/RV storage, and community clubhouse for hosting community events.
This beautiful home comes equipped with all black appliances (refrigerator, stove/oven, hood vent, dishwasher, garbage disposal, and washer/dryer hook ups).
The home features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, loads of cabinet space in a spacious kitchen to cook up homemade meals.
Your own private yard and the safety and security of your own private entrance to your home, plus no shared walls!
On and Off-street parking as well as overflow parking areas for when you have guests.
Here at Yes Communities and Groveland Manor we pride ourselves on offering Gold Key Services (Preventative/Routine/Emergency Services).
